          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "# Telos\n**Advanced app lifecycle manager for jailbroken iOS.**\n\nTake full control over how your apps behave in the background with a priority-based, mutually exclusive system. Choose from three intelligent modes that determine exactly what happens when an app leaves the foreground.\n",
          "useRawFormat": true
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionSpacerView",
          "spacing": 8
