        {
          "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
          "title": "Features"
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
          "markdown": "- **Prevent Suspension** – Keeps apps fully alive, never suspended.\n- **Prevent Termination** – Allows suspension but protects against system kills.\n- **Fast Freeze** – Instantly freezes apps when they leave the foreground, blocking background tasks and saving battery.\n\nModes are enforced exclusively:\n- Apps in **Prevent Suspension** cannot be in any other mode.\n- **Prevent Termination** takes priority over **Fast Freeze**.\n\nAll changes are applied in real time — no respring needed. A single Darwin notification refreshes the configuration dynamically.",
